<p class="ql-align-center">其中便包括苍鹭</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200917/fbc903042ed641ca9e93147ca34f9ac7.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">苍鹭又名</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">灰鹳、青庄、灰鹭</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">有的地方还叫它</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>“长脖老等”</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">“长脖”好理解</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">你看它腿长、嘴长、脖子长</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>妥妥一个“文青美男”</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200917/85a6e6e2c70e4242a4482cd1dec329b3.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">苍鹭颜值方面没说的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">吃亏就吃亏在“衣服”上</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一身灰色总感觉脏兮兮的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">没有对比就没有伤害</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">请看人家白鹭</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200917/d550394f2e5b4476b1b1cbfc1564cfc6.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">是不是显得高贵许多</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">人靠衣服马靠鞍</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">真是这么回事</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200917/47235d2be155481b80a92d76287de7f7.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">至于“老等”</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">据说苍鹭有时站在一个地方</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">等候食物</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">长达数小时之久</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">故得此名</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">大概就是这种状态</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200917/01474b2d6aed4431bfaab9fe273411c5.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">挺拔的身姿</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">威严的神情</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">似乎在告诉游鱼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>“咋，和我耗上了</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>看咱俩谁的耐心大</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>你有本事别出来</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>憋死你”</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200917/c0e15d4c82484808a48f44b31be97c04.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">也许等得太久</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">旁边一只苍鹭不高兴了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">兄弟让让，这块地盘是我的。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">凭啥是你的？写你名字了？</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">两只苍鹭立即吵了起来</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200917/2433745fc3a449c9a39058e07af51db3.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">吵吵闹闹解决不了问题</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">它们决定“斗舞”</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一个号称参加过《这就是街舞》节目</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一个表示郭富城是它的师傅</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">誓要分出个胜负</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">来，放music，炸街的那种</p>
